			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="Shadowheart comments upon a statue of Selûne, located somewhat incongruously in a camp full of goblin marauders. Shadowheart is a little perturbed by the statue's presence, but quickly dismissive of it. Selûne is a rival to her own goddess; the statue deserves an ignominious fate. If Shadowheart is not know to be a Shar worshipper, she's a little more reserved in her comments." />
